        <mxCell id="JVjxVzFQal__MUtopD3h-6" parent="1" style="sketch=0;points=[[0,0,0],[0.25,0,0],[0.5,0,0],[0.75,0,0],[1,0,0],[0,1,0],[0.25,1,0],[0.5,1,0],[0.75,1,0],[1,1,0],[0,0.25,0],[0,0.5,0],[0,0.75,0],[1,0.25,0],[1,0.5,0],[1,0.75,0]];outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#DD344C;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=12;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.payment_cryptography;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="127.75" width="127.75" x="796.13" y="2697.62" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="JVjxVzFQal__MUtopD3h-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;autosizeText=0;fontSize=6;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Experiment 9&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ticket Booking System&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Aim: To design a scalabe platform that allow the users to book and discover tickets for various movies, concerts and live events.&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. Users should be able to search an event based on some title, location and date.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;2. Users should be able to view the details and description of the events like seat availability, details, metadata (like duration, cast and ratings etc)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. Users should be able to book the ticket for the show if tickets/seat are available.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Non Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. System should support 100 Million&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;DAU&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Daily Active Users&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;2. CAP Theorem:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;System should be highly available when users are searching or viewing an event.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;System should be highly consistent with respect to booking a specific ticket.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. System should have a low latency and should response in miliseconds.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Core Entities&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;User: Identity and profile information.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Event: The actual show/movie/concert.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Show: A specific instance of an event.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Seat: Individual units within a venue linked to a Show.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Booking: The transaction linking a User to a Seat.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;API Design&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. Users &amp;amp; Auth:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;POST: /api/v1/auth/signup&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;POST: /api/v1/auth/login&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/users/profile [User profile &amp;amp; booking history]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;2. Discovery (Events &amp;amp; Shows):&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/events [Search with filters: title, city, date]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/events/{event_id} [Comprehensive event details &amp;amp; metadata]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/events/{event_id}/shows [List of shows for a specific event]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/shows/{show_id}/seats [Real-time seat availability map]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. Booking &amp;amp; Transactions:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;POST: /api/v1/bookings/reserve [Temporary lock on seats for 5-10 mins]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;POST: /api/v1/bookings/confirm [Finalize booking after payment]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/bookings/{booking_id} [Check booking status/get e-ticket]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;DELETE: /api/v1/bookings/{booking_id} [Cancel booking/release seats]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;4. Venues:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/venues/{venue_id} [Venue details and location]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GET: /api/v1/venues/{venue_id}/layout [Static seat map structure]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Database Schema Design&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1. Users Table&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;user_id (UUID, PK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;name, email, password_hash&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;created_at (Timestamp)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;2. Events Table&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;event_id (UUID, PK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;title (Varchar, Indexed)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;description (Text)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;metadata (JSONB) [Stores: cast, duration, language, ratings]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;3. Shows Table&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;show_id (UUID, PK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;event_id (FK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;venue_id (FK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;start_time (Timestamp, Indexed)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;city (Varchar, Shard Key)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;4. Show_Seats Table (The Transactional Table)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;show_seat_id (UUID, PK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;show_id (FK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;seat_number (Varchar)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;status (Enum: Available, Locked, Booked)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;price (Decimal)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;version (Int) [For Optimistic Locking]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;5. Bookings Table&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;booking_id (UUID, PK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;user_id (FK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;show_id (FK)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;status (Enum: Pending, Confirmed, Cancelled)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;booking_time (Timestamp)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1620" width="980" x="-90" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="JVjxVzFQal__MUtopD3h-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=24;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;Name: Aditya Singh&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;UID: 23BCS11827&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;Section: KRG-2B&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="340" x="1100" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
